message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $11500. I believe this is a fair price considering the value it offers. What do you think?
Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. I'm interested in the product, but I can only go up to $9000. Let me know if you can work with that.

Bob, I appreciate your interest in the product, but $9000 is unfortunately too low for me.  I'm willing to come down to $10500. This still leaves some room for profit, but I'm confident you'll find the value of the product worth this price.
